sub_title: PhD Student, Wageningen University and Research
summary:
Food Biotechnologist 

Have experience on lab techniques such as DNA isolation, Cre-Lox system for Cloning, PCR, qPCR, Electrophoresis, and Flow Cytometry. 
Also have worked with softwares and websites such as Clone Manger basic 9:0, OLIGO 6, BLAST, , NCBI and KEGG.

Apart from professional work, was also involved in project evaluation, project implementation and participated in evaluation of CV's and proposals.
